author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 
 
Check out the full three-song session of The xx from 2017 on our channel. #VaultSessions #TheCurrent #Thexx
title: The xx perform "On Hold" at The Current studio in 2017 #Thexx

author: The Current
description: WHY NOT’s Henry Breen found inspiration for this playfully complex and speedy electro rocker, “IT’S FUN,” while traveling on the highway. Find it on the trio’s 2025 album “Collection,” featuring an assortment of singles from the band’s catalogue. Breen is also a producer and/or mix engineer for many of the Twin Cities’ brightest young talents, including Samia, Xina, Huhroon, Ava Levy and more. Hit Play!
title: Henry Breen of WHY NOT talks about "IT'S FUN" #WHYNOT #TwinCities
